<i>Let's begin it.</i>

00:09.041 --> 00:10.875
<i>♪ Hoo-hoo-hoo</i>
<i>Hoo-hoo-hoo-hoo-hoo-hoo ♪</i>

00:10.959 --> 00:12.458
<i>♪ Hoo-hoo-hoo-hoo-hoo ♪</i>

